==Russian==

===Etymology===
Deliberate misspelling of Russian [[по-]] ("a bit") + [[дно]] ("bottom") + the misspelling of the diminutive suffix '''-ок''', plural '''-ки'''.

===Noun===
'''падонак''' (padónak) {{m}}

# [[w:Padonki|padonki]] (Internet [[riff-raff]], see the plural form [[падонки|падо́нки]].)

